sentences.sentence: When detergent washing, agitation or impingement provides the best results.
sentences.translation: 在去垢剂洗涤时，搅拌或冲击能得到最好的效果。

sentences.sentence: Shoulder impingement syndrome is one of the most common painful shoulder disorders.
sentences.translation: 肩夹击症候群是一种常见的疼痛性肩关节疾病。

sentences.sentence: In both studies, neck-on-cup impingement was the cause of the observed reduction in ROM.
sentences.translation: 在二者的研究中，髋臼内杯创伤是导致看到的活动度降低。
